title: Swervedriver live albums and b-sides; Juggernaut Rides
description:
This is a collection of mostly live tracks downloaded (free--how cool is that??) from www.swervedriver.com . You can go there to get them, or you can just download this. I've also included Juggernaut Rides--a great double CD greatest hits collection. Swervedriver were one of the best shoegazer bands, and an excellent live band.  

If you like this band go out and buy their albums!
